        "latex": "Soit $z$ et $w$ deux nombres complexes. Démontrer que \\begin{eqnarray*}\r\n                               |z+w|^2&=&|z|^2+2\\Re (z\\overline{w})+|w|^2\\\\\r\n                               |z+w|^2+|z-w|^2&=&2(|z|^2+|w|^2)\\\\\r\n                               |z+w|&\\leq& |z|+|w|\\\\\r\n                               ||z|-|w||&\\leq&|z-w|.\r\n                               \\end{eqnarray*}",
        "html": "<p>Soit <span class=\"math inline\">\\(z\\)</span> et <span class=\"math inline\">\\(w\\)</span> deux nombres complexes. Démontrer que <span class=\"math display\">\\[\\begin{aligned}\n                               |z+w|^2&amp;=&amp;|z|^2+2\\Re (z\\overline{w})+|w|^2\\\\\n                               |z+w|^2+|z-w|^2&amp;=&amp;2(|z|^2+|w|^2)\\\\\n                               |z+w|&amp;\\leq&amp; |z|+|w|\\\\\n                               ||z|-|w||&amp;\\leq&amp;|z-w|.\n                               \\end{aligned}\\]</span></p>\n"
      }
